review.comment: I am an emergency medicine physician in Florida and had a legal issue this year.   Musca Law and Mr. John Musca have helped me tremendously,  and was able to get resolution of the issue in a timely and professional manner.  The final outcome is still pending, however everything is progressing as they planned, and their professionalism is outstanding.  I recommend  Musca Law to any professional who encounters this unfortunate circumstance.
